{"tid":580081,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[是日午餐] 自製香料雞肉貝殼粉","createTime":"2018-03-04T07:35:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T19:46:46.000Z","uid":43041,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a3d3c889954c547859c680c487580996c2c9ba56","tid":580081,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:35:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/150032_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F04%2F150032_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d135b63b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n切燈籠椒洋蔥<br />\n雞上脾肉斬件，切一啖大細，醃雞<br />\n醃料（分量目測）：salt, pepper, chili powder, cumin, and garlic powder<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/151336_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F04%2F151336_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2495db52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n炒熟雞肉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/152221_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F04%2F152221_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=49321845&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拎起<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/152231_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F04%2F152231_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e80b9cab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n剩低既雞油炒洋蔥燈籠椒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/152331_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F04%2F152331_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=af186a50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n倒埋雞肉入去炒，落多少少cumin, and garlic powder, paprika，炒香<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/152443_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F04%2F152443_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7b0219fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n倒入水同雞湯，滾左後落貝殼粉<br />\nbtw我係度落多左雞湯，鹹左小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/152634_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F04%2F152634_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d19e9fa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n滾到咁上下落忌廉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/152703_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F04%2F152703_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5b431b8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明明實物係深色d再黃d，唔知點解影出黎咁白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n煮到意粉熟同個汁收水變醬，鍾意可以加芝士<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/152734_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F04%2F152734_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=968d695a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今次無食譜<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉屌 煮完先覺得碟野好肥"},{"pid":"8677891afc0a4f6badd12c2710f243de48ece082","tid":580081,"uid":6562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:38:07.000Z","msg":"一定要加椒嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b8